  (hiœÜ : ‚àÄ·∂† i in l, ‚à´ x, œÜ i x ‚àÇŒº = 1) -- todo: we could weaken this to "the integral tends to 1"
  (hœÜ : tendsto (Œª n, support (œÜ n)) l (ùìù 0).small_sets)
